# 💰 Expense Dashboard

A clean and interactive web-based expense tracking dashboard built using Flask.

## 🚀 Features

* Add daily expenses with category and date
* View total expenses and transaction count
* Automatic top category detection
* Visual breakdown using pie chart (Chart.js)
* Filter and manage expense records
* Clean modern UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Backend: Flask (Python)
* Frontend: HTML, CSS
* Charts: Chart.js
* Database: SQLite

## 📱 Live Demo

👉 https://expense-dashboard.onrender.com

